原始數值

lm.palette <- colorRampPalette(c( "white","orange","red"), space = "rgb")
spplot(Popn_TWN, zcol="ELDERLY_RATIO", col.regions=lm.palette(20))

LISA map (P-value < 0.05)

Popn_TWN.nb.w <- nb2listw(Popn_TWN.nb, zero.policy = T)
LISA <- localmoran(Popn_TWN$ELDERLY_RATIO, Popn_TWN.nb.w, zero.policy = T, alternative = "two.sided")

diff <- Popn_TWN$ELDERLY_RATIO - mean(Popn_TWN$ELDERLY_RATIO)
z <- LISA[, 4]

quad <- c() #don't use vector
quad[diff > 0 & z > 0] <- 1 #H-H
quad[diff < 0 & z > 0] <- 2 #L-L
quad[diff > 0 & z < 0] <- 3 #H-L
quad[diff < 0 & z < 0] <- 4 #L-H
quad[LISA[, 5] > 0.05] <- 5

color <- c("red", "blue", "lightpink", "lightblue", "grey", rgb(0.95, 0.95, 0.95))
plot(Popn_TWN, border = "grey", col = color[quad], main = "LISA Map", xlim = c(170000, 180000), ylim = c(2440000, 2800000))
legend("bottomleft", legend = c("HH", "LL", "HL", "LH", "NS"), fill = color, bty = "n", y.intersp = 1, x.intersp = 1)

Gi*

Popn_TWN.nb.in <- include.self(Popn_TWN.nb)
Popn_TWN.nb.w.in <- nb2listw(Popn_TWN.nb.in)
Gi <- localG(Popn_TWN$ELDERLY_RATIO, Popn_TWN.nb.w.in)
LG <- as.vector(Gi)

quad <- c()
quad[LG >= 1.645] = 1 #cluster
quad[LG < 1.645] = 2 #non-cluster

color <- c("red", "grey")
plot(Popn_TWN, border = "grey", col = color[quad], main = "Cluster Map", xlim = c(170000, 180000), ylim = c(2440000, 2800000))
legend("bottomleft", c("Cluster", "Non-cluster"), fill = color, bty = "n", y.intersp = 1, x.intersp = 1)
